.container
  h1 NPM Modules
  h2.group-heading Web
  .modules
    a.module(href = "https://popupable.ewanhowell.com", target = "_blank")
      h2 popupable
      p A lightweight, zero-dependency lightbox library using modern JavaScript and CSS, with support for galleries, zoom, and pinch gestures.
    a.module(href = "https://easy-tooltips.ewanhowell.com", target = "_blank")
      h2 easy-tooltips
      p A lightweight, zero-dependency tooltip library using modern JavaScript and CSS, with data-attribute configuration and keyboard support.
    a.module(href = "https://fluid-marquee.ewanhowell.com", target = "_blank")
      h2 fluid-marquee
      p A lightweight, zero-dependency marquee/scrolling content library using modern JavaScript and CSS.
  h2.group-heading Node
  .modules
    a.module(href = "https://www.npmjs.com/package/block-model-renderer", target = "_blank")
      h2 block-model-renderer
      p Minecraft block and item model rendering for Node.js, supporting textures, animations, and custom display settings.
    a.module(href = "https://www.npmjs.com/package/headless-three", target = "_blank")
      h2 headless-three
      p Headless Three.js rendering for Node.js, made simple — render 3D scenes server-side with WebGL.
    a.module(href = "https://www.npmjs.com/package/headless-three-gltf", target = "_blank")
      h2 headless-three-gltf
      p A GLTFLoader for headless-three, adding support for loading GLTF and GLB models in a headless Three.js environment.
    a.module(href = "https://www.npmjs.com/package/skia-canvas-draw-text", target = "_blank")
      h2 skia-canvas-draw-text
      p A function to make drawing text easier with skia-canvas, supporting wrapping, alignment, gravity, and shadows.
    a.module(href = "https://www.npmjs.com/package/simple-gtts", target = "_blank")
      h2 simple-gtts
      p A simple Google text-to-speech wrapper for Node.js for generating spoken audio from text.
  h2.group-heading Universal
  .modules
    a.module(href = "https://www.npmjs.com/package/easyjsontools", target = "_blank")
      h2 easyjsontools
      p Tools for working with JSON objects, including utilities for cleaning and ensuring JSON structure.
    a.module(href = "https://www.npmjs.com/package/emoji-info", target = "_blank")
      h2 emoji-info
      p A library to get detailed information about emojis, including names, categories, and metadata.
